{"word":"G75 - ἀγωνίζομαι - agōnízomai - ag-o-nid'-zom-ahee - Fight","slug":"G75","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀγωνίζομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>agōnízomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ag-o-nid'-zom-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Fight"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03B3;&#x03C9;&#x03BD;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - ago&#x0304;nizomai</b> - <i>ag-o-nid'-zom-ahee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G73\">G73</a>; to <i>struggle</i>, literally (to <i>compete</i> for a prize), figuratively (to <i>contend</i> with an adversary), or generally (to <i>endeavor</i> to accomplish something): - fight, labor fervently, strive."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1864\">G1864</a>, <a href=\"#/G2610\">G2610</a>, <a href=\"#/G464\">G464</a>, <a href=\"#/G73\">G73</a>, <a href=\"#/G74\">G74</a>"}]}